        <p class="text-amber-700 font-medium">△ Initially worried about threshold but role is on Shortage Occupation List, so 80% rate applies. CoS took longer than expected (3 weeks). Now working, but NHS GP registration took a month in new area. Added IMG Global for interim coverage.</p>
